Path: Examples
Content:
Get e raised to the power of zero
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0 | math exp
1.0

```
Get e (same as 'math e')
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1 | math exp
2.718281828459045

```
